      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOT A SCAN (6) comes off an average run last start when seventh at this track over 390m behind Paw Kattia (22.70) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Key runner on her best form. GOLD GIZMO (2) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at Healesville over 300m behind Sandy Cheek (17.24) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Solid formlines coming through his last run. One of the better hopes. ALPHA GIRL (1) jumped from an outside draw but scored by half a length (22.90) at Warrnambool in Bottom Up - Grade 5. Is yet to find the frame here from three. Likely to be in the finish. ESPECIAL YOGI (5) looks an each-way chance.",
